Jane Eyre is a 2011 British romantic drama film directed by Cary Fukunaga and starring Mia Wasikowska and Michael Fassbender .
The screenplay is written by Moira Buffini based on the 1847 novel of the same name by Charlotte BrontÃ« .
The film was released on 11 March 2011 in the United States and 9 September in Great Britain and Ireland .